#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:108
msgid "`ptool.semver.bump(v, op[, channel])` returns a new version object after applying the bump."
msgstr "`ptool.semver.bump(v, op[, channel])` devuelve un nuevo objeto de versión tras aplicar el incremento."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:111
msgid "`v` (string|Version, required): The original version."
msgstr "`v` (string|Version, obligatorio): La versión original."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:112
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:112"
msgid "`op` (string, required): One of `major`, `minor`, `patch`, `release`, `alpha`, `beta`, `rc`, `prepatch`, `preminor`, or `premajor`."
msgstr "`op` (string, obligatorio): Uno de `major`, `minor`, `patch`, `release`, `alpha`, `beta`, `rc`, `prepatch`, `preminor` o `premajor`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:114
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:114"
msgid "`channel` (string, optional): Supported only for `prepatch`, `preminor`, and `premajor`. Must be one of `alpha`, `beta`, or `rc`. Defaults to `alpha`."
msgstr "`channel` (string, opcional): Solo se admite para `prepatch`, `preminor` y `premajor`. Debe ser `alpha`, `beta` o `rc`. Por defecto es `alpha`."

